uk.ac.bristol.star.feather
Interface Reader<T>

public interface Reader<T>

Reads a value from a given slot of a feather column. The getObject(int) method will supply a typed value; multiple other primitive-typed methods are provided so that object creation can be avoided if the primitive type is known, but note that not all of these will give sensible results for all column types.

Since:
26 Feb 2020
